data.description: This beautiful home in Grey Hawk Estates has ample space for everyone! The 4 bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs provides convenience and comfort, with the 5th bedroom and another bath downstairs that works perfectly for guests, next gen or young adult living. The huge bonus room is a versatile space that can be used as a game room, home theater or fitness room. The loft space is another flexible area that can serve as a cozy reading nook, a study, or a play area for kids. This home sits in a quiet neighborhood off a cul-de-sac. The private, fully fenced backyard with wooded views adds a sense of serenity and natural beauty to the property. The screened lanai is a great feature for enjoying the outdoors without worrying about bugs or bad weather, and a perfect spot for al fresco dining or relaxation. The pavered patio, outdoor pool and deck invites you to enjoy the outdoors. St. Augustine is a vibrant community known for its historic charm and beautiful beaches. This fantastic home offers... a combination of space and privacy while being close to all the amenities and attractions that the area has to offer!
